{"tid":624281,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"（關愛座露底了） 關狗五毛屈毛技倆出現了","createTime":"2018-04-10T16:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T19:54:13.000Z","uid":99568,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d7790c6e5387188a584513b5276db32fee5d3a","tid":624281,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"關愛狗多次喺我既post留言屈我係五毛, 但係又解釋唔到點解我係佢口中既五毛, 跟住 我就反問佢 叫佢想屈我毛都比啲原因, 跟住佢就 用下面第二呢張圖屈我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/004443_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F004443_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e763301e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/004451_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F004451_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4d0493f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢張咁嘅假膠都講得出係五毛證據, <br />\n我個假膠留言就喺度話 （你還有黨信不信我還有你，反正我信了）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然關愛座話 我呢個留言唔係假膠, 我想睇下各位連登仔點睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 中資股大股東關狗</span>"},{"pid":"a1c23e08d2ed3d36f662322863924b106919134b","tid":624281,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"關狗偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" cla